$ Csound: performance pass
@ peformance pass

aka: perf-pass

Performance passes have a regular schedule which is controlled by `kr`.

During a performance pass, the → Kunst/Musik/Csound/processing-chain is traversed.

A perf-pass updates k-variables and the elements of the a-variable arrays.

sa:
  → Kunst/Musik/Csound/init-pass
